    "In 1931, she completed her degree, and published her dissertation titled <em>Voraussetzungen und Entwicklung des mittelalterlichen St\u00e4dtebaus in Deutschland</em> (Determinants and development of medieval urban planning in Germany) under the (second) Vienna School scholar <a href=\"/strzygowskij\">Josef Strzygowski</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Because of her Jewish heritage, Lang was persecuted and forced to flee Austria after the Anschluss of 1938.": [],
